description.en: Qovar offers its users to get profit with the help of P-o-S mining. The profit is 10% annually + commissions from the transactions your wallet will confirm. QC price growth is not included in the income. To get the reward from mining, you need to register a web wallet, buy QC coins, transfer the coins to the desktop wallet and keep it online as long as possible. You no longer have to spend money on miners and video cards. Depending on the wallet balance, reward is deposited daily.
